description:
FriendInvites  

Create and manage Discord friend invite links with simple commands!
*P.S. This is using an official but unreleased and undocumented Discord feature. Things may break at any time and I may not be able to fix said broken thing.*
*P.P.S. These friend invite links look like normal Discord invites! Be careful of automod in servers.*

Download: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spinfal/enmity-plugins/master/dist/FriendInvites.js
Source: https://github.com/spinfal/enmity-plugins/tree/master/FriendInvites
